In January 2023 [bitomic](https://github.com/bitomic), [Kohki
Miki](https://github.com/giginet), [Paul-Émile](https://github.com/pebou),
[tillfox](https://github.com/tillfox) scraped generation 9 data from the web
and added it here.
* Generation 8 data is scraped from [different resources](https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Generation_VIII) which are considered to be trustful.
